bakery: bakery (C++ Framework for GNOME)
bakery:
bakery: Bakery is a C++ Framework for creating  GNOME applications using 
bakery: gtkmm.  It provides a library for a Document/View architecture, XML 
bakery: as a Document storage format, an easy to start developing GNOME 
bakery: applications, and contains a few utility classes.
